Artemis

Automatic Regression Test Environment and Measurement Instrument System

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Build.PL
	./Build
	./Build test
	./Build install



Start TAP receiver
------------------

 * bin/artemis-reports-receiver


Submit report
-------------

* Manually:

    $ nc -q0 localhost 7357
      OK 1 foo
      OK 2 bar
      OK 3 baz
      ^D


* Simple scripted:

    $ (echo "OK 1 foo" ; echo "OK 2 bar"; echo "OK 3 baz") |       nc -q0 localhost 7357
    $ (echo "OK 1 foo" ; echo "OK 2 bar"; echo "OK 3 baz") | tee | nc -q0 localhost 7357


* Submit a TAP emitting testrun from a harness:

    $ prove -vl t/artemis_schema_testrundb.t |       nc -q0 localhost 7357
    $ prove -vl t/artemis_schema_testrundb.t | tee | nc -q0 localhost 7357


* Submit a TAP emitting testrun without harness:

    $ perl -Ilib t/artemis_schema_testrundb.t |       nc -q0 localhost 7357
    $ perl -Ilib t/artemis_schema_testrundb.t | tee | nc -q0 localhost 7357


